{"tid":2375987,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"笑撚死2021年有個ig page賣$1/一部macbook都仲有人信","createTime":"2021-01-22T12:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T10:21:51.000Z","uid":70878,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3aa15692cae1b9093007b7894673021f88d7d497","tid":2375987,"uid":70878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:13:25.000Z","msg":"成班傻仔幫人免費谷followers都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說呢兩日有個新ig page: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/top_gadget_hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftop_gadget_hk%2F&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TfE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=2a504d74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/top_gadget_hk/</a><br />\n聲稱<br />\n「🙇🏻&zwj;♂️小店新開張 希望多d人認識我地🙇🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n本店現舉辦一次超豐富的有獎活動<br />\n獎品包括：<br />\n只有🏆大獎 - Macbook Pro 13吋太空灰 1TB with Touch ID (最少5️⃣份)<br />\n大家反應好會再加碼🙋🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n每部價值 HKD14,699<br />\n參加方法非常簡單，<br />\n1️⃣ Follow我地嘅IG➕Like呢個Post☑️⁣<br />\n2️⃣ Tag 2位朋友☑️⁣<br />\n3️⃣ Repost呢個post係你嘅Story到☑️⁣<br />\n（記得Cap低story嘅圖！中獎我地會要求出示證明🤓）⁣<br />\n4️⃣ 去我地Profile Bio第一條link 填寫聯絡電郵📧以便得獎時通知你<br />\n」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pRzqwan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpRzqwan.jpg&h=bd3ad88e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開善堂咩屌，仲係stories話想加碼送夠10部<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地連間公司名都冇<br />\n點樣入貨？唔洗交稅？點樣代理？就咁係ig開個page就可以賣野？<br />\n<br />\nP.s. 想問佢地咁做有冇犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>網上抽獎也違法？<br />\n相信有很多商界朋友都有舉辦一些活動來推廣生意，而近年利用facebook舉辦抽獎活動來宣傳更是大行其道,因為實在方便快捷,成本低,成效高！<br />\n<br />\n但眾多好處背後，又有沒有隱憂及風險？<br />\n近期就有一些企業或人仕因為在facebook舉辦抽獎活動，而涉嫌違反《賭博條例》，被控以組織非法獎券活動罪。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例《賭博條例》(第148章)，凡公司舉辦比賽來推廣業務，而該比賽帶有博彩成分(例如抽獎或擦卡之類)，便須領有推廣生意的競賽牌照，否則一經定罪後，最高可被罰款HK$50,000 及監禁 2 年。<br />\n<br />\n大家可向民政事務總署牌照事務處申請「推廣生意的競賽牌照」，需時大概7個工作天，簽發牌照費用為HK$1,590。<br />\n領取牌照後，你就可以開始舉辦有關競賽。競賽結束後，你必須在本地的中文及英文報章各一份公布競賽結果，並把有關剪報的副本送交民政事務局局長委派的公職人員。<br />\n<br />\n有部份企業想免卻申請牌照的麻煩，於是便避開有博彩成分的遊戲，改為以技巧競爭的遊戲取代，例如：問答比賽、Mini Game比賽、命題比賽等&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n隨著科技進步，大家可更輕鬆地推廣及發展業務，但大家對法律的知識卻相對不足。我們建議大家可聘用律師對公司的日常運作給專業建議及監察，此舉可大大減低觸犯法例的風險，這對公司的利益、發展及商譽也大有裨益。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.yaa.com.hk/en/%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%8A%BD%E7%8D%8E%E4%B9%9F%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yaa.com.hk%2Fen%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%258A%25BD%25E7%258D%258E%25E4%25B9%259F%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%25B3%2595%25EF%25BC%259F%2F&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TfE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=58bb4f9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yaa.com.hk/en/%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%8A%BD%E7%8D%8E%E4%B9%9F%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9F/</a>"},{"pid":"3513cabc73ef621d5d115de214b44b48d451730f","tid":2375987,"uid":70878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:16:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b6520904309c59c61598fb912d42c34e5d5048","tid":2375987,"uid":70878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c896e72a4afb526890c28d26229400bc05e40291","tid":2375987,"uid":136416,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:26:59.000Z","msg":"樓主曲線宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f3529665fa1643b57c807fa6094ee4d40c2125","tid":2375987,"uid":70878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c896e72a4afb526890c28d26229400bc05e40291","tid":2375987,"uid":136416,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:26:59.000Z","msg":"樓主曲線宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor